ActFederal Real Property Act
SubjectSettlement and Release Agreement Canada-Alberta Transfer of mines and minerals
PrecisOrder approving the transfer of administration and control to the Government of Alberta over certain mines and minerals as provided for in a settlement agreement in relation to a constitutional dispute between the Government of Canada and the Government of Alberta concerning ownership over certain of those mines and minerals which are situated within Alberta but held by Canada.
